1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,920
My Lady, you're awake.

4
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,680
Where am I?

5
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:17,040
It... It is Ruyi Palace.

6
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,599
Ruyi Palace?

7
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,239
Why am I in a palace?

8
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,040
I clearly remember

9
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,640
watching the fireworks with Ling Xiao
just yesterday.

10
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,239
I'm going to see Ling Xiao.

11
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,439
We agreed yesterday

12
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,640
to have pupae today.

13
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,239
You still want to see him?

14
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,439
Don't you already know everything?

15
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:42,239
You mean about Jing Liuli?

16
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,840
Everyone has a past.

17
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,319
I don't care about Jing Liuli.

18
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,519
I only care about my future
with Ling Xiao.

19
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,599
Mo Shuo.

20
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:01,439
Ke'er.

21
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:04,040
What's going on with the Princess?

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,200
Why has she lost her recent memories?

23
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:06,920
Ke'er,

24
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:09,120
this is the only way.

25
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,919
It concerns the Princess's safety.

26
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,360
Tell me the truth.

27
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,039
It's the Oblivion Herb.

28
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,280
This is the only way

29
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,039
to erase Mu Ruyi's pain.

30
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,840
Are you trying to kill her?

31
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,159
Mu Ruyi has learned everything.

32
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,319
We can't hide it.

33
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,639
Do you wish to see her
remember everything

34
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,759
but shatter her,

35
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,719
or to protect her from the past
and let her live in peace?

36
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:37,520
Mu Ruyi is bent on dying.

37
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,400
This is the only way to save her.

38
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,759
You looked worn out today,

39
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,680
so I consulted the imperial physician.

40
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,479
He said your old illness
has flared up again,

41
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:52,360
which is why you've lost some memories.

42
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,560
But

43
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,000
I still can't remember anything.

44
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,960
Every little thing

45
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:09,159
about you is in this book.

46
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:12,400
It will all come back to you.

47
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:14,820
(Liu Rushi's Preferences)

48
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:24,500
(She doesn't like salty food,
just add a little vinegar.)

49
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,560
We even encountered rogues

50
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,639
on the way down the mountain?

51
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,439
You took a sword for me.

52
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:40,400
So much happened between us after that!

53
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,000
Look.

54
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,560
On your hand,

55
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,319
the scar from back then is still there.

56
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:53,400
It's just some scratch.

57
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,080
It doesn't hurt anymore.

58
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,360
From now on,

59
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:59,280
we must both take care of ourselves.

60
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,120
No more hurt.

61
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,439
Let's

62
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,520
enjoy some opera by the river,

63
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,520
shall we?

64
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:08,800
Wonderful!

65
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,439
Good.

66
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,759
I'll be waiting.

67
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,199
My Lady,

68
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,639
aren't you supposed to see His Majesty?

69
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,680
Why?

70
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,680
You told me yesterday

71
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,319
that His Majesty was taking you

72
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,079
to the riverside opera today.

73
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:31,399
I don't remember any of this.

74
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,160
It's already this late.

75
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,680
His Majesty must be waiting for you.

76
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,720
She was so excited yesterday,

77
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,319
sharing her plans with me.

78
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,519
Now she has lost all memories.

79
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,079
The Oblivion Herb was meant

80
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,639
to save her life

81
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:58,920
and free her from the past,

82
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,120
but why are her memories and thoughts

83
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,519
so disordered?

84
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,079
What if something bad
really happens to her?

85
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:09,720
Ling Xiao.

86
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:12,680
Rushi,

87
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,439
you're finally here.

88
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,160
Something must be wrong with me today.

89
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:18,439
I totally forgot about the opera.

90
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,199
And I kept you waiting so long.

91
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:21,959
Really?

92
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:24,120
You don't remember any of it?

93
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,600
It's my bad.

94
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,319
No.

95
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:33,160
It's on me.

96
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:36,959
Take a seat.

97
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,480
Something came over me recently.

98
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:46,199
I keep forgetting important things.

99
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:48,160
They're just trivial matters.

100
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,759
I'm here to remember for you.

101
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,680
But you're not by my side

102
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,199
every single moment.

103
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,439
Do you remember the book I gave you?

104
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,600
When I'm not with you,

105
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,120
it will be there in my place.

106
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,879
What a pity.

107
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:10,879
I missed the chance
to watch opera with you.

108
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,680
I love watching opera so much.

109
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,720
It doesn't matter.

110
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,680
How about

111
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,759
I tell you a story?

112
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,839
I'd love that!

113
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,720
Once upon a time,

114
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:28,040
there was a prince
who was unwanted from birth.

115
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,519
He once met a princess
from a rival kingdom.

116
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:32,839
Their first meeting

117
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,639
was also on such a dim, moonlit night.

118
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,240
The prince had set out for revenge,

119
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,000
but the moment he laid eyes on her,

120
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,959
his heart was lost.

121
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:48,240
Though their story began
with blood feuds

122
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,920
and bitter pain,

123
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:52,839
though the start was anything but good,

124
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,120
they still filled their days

125
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,920
with countless beautiful moments.

126
00:06:58,639 --> 00:07:01,480
They talked in the moonlight,

127
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,560
celebrated the Qixi Festival,

128
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,800
made wishes upon shooting stars,

129
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:09,439
and pledged to love each other

130
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,879
until their hair turned white.

131
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:18,240
It seems

132
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,839
my storytelling
works better than calming incense.

133
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:26,940
♪Even if just for a glance♪

134
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,079
(At the gate of the Ruyi Palace,)

135
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,959
(there's a huge stone lion,)

136
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,879
(as fierce-looking as Ling Xiao.)

137
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,600
(No,)

138
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,360
(Ling Xiao's cuter.)

139
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,120
(Add less chili when cooking,)

140
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,519
(or Ling Xiao will be tearing up
from the heat.)

141
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,120
(Liu Rushi,)

142
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:49,439
(more memories are slipping away.)

143
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,560
(But you must remember,)

144
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,319
(you want to be with Ling Xiao forever.)

145
00:07:57,420 --> 00:08:01,620
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

146
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,639
I'm sorry.

147
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,800
I shouldn't have treated you this way.

148
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:12,380
♪Those years we shared
through joy and pain♪

149
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:17,500
♪When we were fearless, you and me♪

150
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:27,920
Ke'er.

151
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:31,160
Ke'er,

152
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,200
why?

153
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,600
You struck so hard today.

154
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:34,600
If you

155
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,679
don't make things clear today,

156
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,080
then I'll take your life.

157
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,960
What's it about this time?

158
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:42,879
No matter what,

159
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,240
anything concerning Mu Ruyi

160
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,440
is a matter of life and death to me.

161
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,960
The Princess's memory continues to fade.

162
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,240
Is this the effect of the Oblivion Herb?

163
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,960
Are her thoughts frequently disordered?

164
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,120
Does she often forget things?

165
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,600
Exactly.

166
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:58,480
This is the result of taking the Herb
too many times.

167
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,879
The poison has accumulated
and cannot be expelled.

168
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,159
That's why she's showing these symptoms.

169
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,360
You certainly talk well.

170
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,039
All this talk

171
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,200
about saving the Princess from danger,

172
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:09,200
but in fact,
you're the one endangering her.

173
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,200
I'm going to kill Ling Xiao

174
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,720
and let the Prince see the truth.

175
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,080
Mu Ruyi's memory is fading.

176
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,799
Right now,
she trusts Ling Xiao more than anyone.

177
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,919
She won't believe a word we say.

178
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,720
I would never betray the Princess,

179
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,039
much less

180
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,720
treat her life as if it were nothing.

181
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,480
In that case,

182
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:26,919
let's be straightforward

183
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,879
and let her see the truth herself.

184
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:33,840
Mo Shuo.

185
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:35,600
Ruyi's memory

186
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,759
has been getting worse.

187
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,679
She couldn't remember
what we just talked about.

188
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,080
Your Majesty,

189
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,200
these are signs of
the Oblivion Herb poisoning.

190
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,240
She's taken it multiple times,

191
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,200
and with her overwhelming anxiety,

192
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,360
that's what's causing these symptoms.

193
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,799
Are you saying

194
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,919
that I've ended up hurting her instead?

195
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,320
I didn't mean it that way.

196
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,440
The situation was urgent.

197
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,600
The Oblivion Herb was our only option.

198
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,720
As for the situation now,

199
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,840
it's beyond our expectations.

200
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,000
The Oblivion Herb?

201
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,840
All this time, I thought

202
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:12,600
it was just my old illness flaring up.

203
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:17,039
I never imagined he was behind it.

204
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:22,519
Your Majesty,

205
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,879
should we keep her on the Herb?

206
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,720
When I first gave it to her,

207
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,159
I didn't want her to recall

208
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,519
our painful past.

209
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,480
But the poison is accumulating.

210
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,279
Her life matters most.

211
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,799
I understand Your Majesty
is trying to make it good.

212
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:45,960
But

213
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,080
despite the harmony and love

214
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,039
you share now,

215
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,399
if she discovers

216
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,960
you've been deceiving her,

217
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,000
she'll hurt even more.

218
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,039
I've made up my mind.

219
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,399
My well-intentioned protection

220
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,440
will only end up harming us both.

221
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:09,840
I should leave the final choice to her,

222
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,679
rather than taking her memories away

223
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,360
in the name of caring

224
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:18,159
and leaving her in an unreal happiness.

225
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,080
It is good that Your Majesty
has thought this through.

226
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,960
That would be ideal.

227
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:27,279
(So all that I once cherished)

228
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:31,120
(was a carefully crafted lie.)

229
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,960
My Lady, it's time for your medicine.

230
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,440
Just leave it here.

231
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,240
I'll take it later.

232
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:53,320
My Lady, please take it while it's warm.

233
00:11:57,519 --> 00:11:58,240
Okay.

234
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,639
You may leave.
